Kapere was a former Executive Chairperson of the Namibia National Youth Council. The cause of his death has not been reported. The president described the legislator as an "illustrious youth leader". He tweeted that the late Kapere had played an important role of shaping the youth leadership in Namibia: I have learned with sadness about the passing of our illustrious youth leader, Cde Mandela Kapere. Our nation has lost a dynamic Parliamentarian who played an important role in shaping the trajectory of youth leadership in our land. Sincere condolences to the entire family.